headline: Equifax Canada collaborating to help protect Canadians against scams
summary: – Equifax Canada joins forces with more than 40 other leading businesses and government agencies –TORONTO, Nov. 21, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Equifax Canada has joined the Canadian Anti-Scam Coalition to provide its industry leadership and expertise to help fight financial crime.
